REAndroid/APKEditor.Changelog:
## What's Changed
* Default internal dex library
* Update README.md documentation by @yonggamer in https://github.com/REAndroid/APKEditor/pull/191
* update execution logs by @yonggamer in https://github.com/REAndroid/APKEditor/pull/192
* translation by @Kirlif in https://github.com/REAndroid/APKEditor/pull/193
* Fix duplicate `res/` directory in APK refactor output by @AbhiTheModder in https://github.com/REAndroid/APKEditor/pull/195
* Decode/encode dex profile (binaries under asset/dexopt)
* Ensure data is fully transferred between channels by @janisozaur in https://github.com/REAndroid/ARSCLib/pull/85
* Using ARSCLib 1.3.8

## New Contributors
* @yonggamer made their first contribution in https://github.com/REAndroid/APKEditor/pull/191
* @janisozaur made their first contribution in https://github.com/REAndroid/ARSCLib/pull/85

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/REAndroid/APKEditor/compare/V1.4.3...V1.4.4
